		<h1 class="p-opener__hed p-opener__hed--small wp-block-post-title">Florida Is Executing Prisoners at a Record Pace, Even as Most of the U.S. Abandons the Death Penalty</h1>

					
<h2 class="p-opener__dek wp-block-propublica-dek">
	Early last year, Gov. Ron DeSantis began signing death warrants at a faster rate than ever before. What followed was the most intense period of executions the state has carried out in more than eight decades.</h2>

